# External libraries

## qrcodegen

Source: https://github.com/nayuki/QR-Code-generator

The `qrcodegen/` folder is a wrapper for the library, to include the c sources from `qrcodegen-src/c`.
I didn't use PlatformIO's config `lib_extra_dirs` because it builds all files in the folder.
Had to use `lib_ignore` because it was including `qrcodegen-src` which has no header files.

Initialize submodule:
```shell
git submodule update --init
```

Update qrcodegen to a new release:
```shell
git -C lib/qrcodegen-src checkout <new-tag>
git add lib/qrcodegen-src
git commit -m "chore: update qrcodegen to <new-tag>"
```
